- Root-cause component: docker_004 (container)
- Root-cause occurrence datetime (Asia/Shanghai, UTC+8): 2020-05-22 01:37:00+08:00 (first observed docker_004 trace anomalies in the incident window; the most extreme JDBC latency spike was later at 2020-05-22 01:53:00+08)
